<H2><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C"><B>HYMN OF VESPERS FROM PASSOVER TO ASCENSION </B></FONT></H2>
<H3><PRE>

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Am              G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   TO THE LAMB'S SUPPER,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                   Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   ROBED IN WHITE ROBES,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   F
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   HAVING CROSSED THE RED SEA,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                            E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   LET'S SING TO CHRIST THE LORD.
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Am                  G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   His body burned of love
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                            Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   is a living bread on the table;
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                       G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   His blood upon the altar
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                           Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   is the cup of the new covenant.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Am              G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   TO THE LAMB'S SUPPER,
