</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   HAVING CROSSED THE RED SEA,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                            E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   LET'S SING TO CHRIST THE LORD.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Am                  G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   In this wonderful vespers
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                       Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   the ancient wonders return:
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                      G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   a mighty arm saves us
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                         Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   from the destructive angel.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Am              G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   TO THE LAMB'S SUPPER,
