</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   Meek lamb sacrificed
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                     Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   Christ is our Passover
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   His adorable body
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                          Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   is the true unleavened bread.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Am              G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   TO THE LAMB'S SUPPER,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                   Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   ROBED IN WHITE ROBES,
