</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   LET'S SING TO CHRIST THE LORD.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Am                    G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   Praise and honor to Christ
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                   Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   victorious over death,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                                   G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   to the Father and to the Holy Spirit
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                Am  G Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   now and forever. AMEN.

